[4] New York (Tioga County)
Date: Fri 23 Mar 2012
Source: WBNG [edited]
http://www.wbng.com/news/local/Tioga-County-Whooping-Cough-Cases-144001286.html

3 people in Tioga County have been diagnosed with pertussis, also known as whooping cough. The Tioga County Health Department reports each person was in a group
setting so it expects the cases of pertussis to increase.

